# =============================================================================
# Mindspace — Vite frontend environment (copy to `.env` in this folder)
# =============================================================================
#
# Supabase Auth + data API (public anon key is safe in the browser; RLS applies).
# Dashboard → Project Settings → API:
#   - Project URL     → VITE_SUPABASE_URL
#   - anon public key → VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
#
# Auth provider: enable “Email” under Authentication → Providers.
# Sign-in uses email + password (Supabase’s built-in flow). Optional “display
# name” on signup is stored in user_metadata only.
#
# After editing .env, restart `npm run dev`.
# =============================================================================

# Mindspace Express API — required on Vercel (production). No trailing slash.
# Production (Render):
#   VITE_API_URL=https://mindspace-j7br.onrender.com
# Local dev (optional; defaults to http://localhost:3000 when unset in dev):
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3000

